"{\"uid\": \"nbclosangeles.com-news-local-how-tom-cruise-pulled-off-olympic-closing-ceremony-stunt-3486713\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Actor Tom Cruise was ready and willing to do the Hollywood sign stunt himself for the Paris Olympics closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 49, \"end\": 63, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Robert Kovacik reports for the NBC4 News at 4 p.m. on Monday, August 12, 2024.\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 119, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Kovacik\", \"score\": 0.9999354262135568, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Robert Kovacik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Kovacik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Kovacik\"}, {\"begin\": 150, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNBC\", \"score\": 0.999999988890295, \"rank\": 1.1109640419285052e-08, \"text\": \"NBC4\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Cruise's jaw-dropping stunt during the Closing Ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympics was the talk of the town as rumors swirled that he had a trick up his sleeve for the big event.\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 199, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What many people may not know, however, is that it was an effort that first took action earlier this year.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a \\\"Mission Impossible\\\" Olympic handoff from Paris to Los Angeles as the 62-year-old actor scaled down the Stade de France to carry the Olympic flag to Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998319709, \"rank\": 1.6800203920466057e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.356346244491172e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.356346244491172e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of the handoff included a pre-taped video of Cruise riding a motorcycle to the Hollywood sign, which was recorded back in March.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream Los Angeles News for free, 24/7, wherever you are.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.356346244491172e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But keeping the stunt a secret?\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was \\\"Risky Business\\\" to conceal the recording.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even our own cameras, our security cameras were turned off and not recording during this stunt,\\\" said Jeff Zarrinnam, Chairman of the Hollywood Sign Trust.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood Sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the camera pans from an up-close shot of Cruise at the Hollywood sign to zoom out for a full view, it's revealed the iconic sign is decorated with the recognizable Olympic rings in the video.\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They just wanted to do something spectacular, something with the Hollywood Sign because the Hollywood Sign represents Los Angeles,\\\" Zarrinnam said.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.356346244491172e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise, who does his own stunts, was ready to be on board when he heard of the idea.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Get Los Angeles's latest local news on crime, entertainment, weather, schools, cost of living and more.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.356346244491172e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's your go-to source for today's LA news.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because Hollywood means so much to him,\\\" the Chairman said.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1688, \"end\": 1697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998352516422, \"rank\": 1.6474823642867453e-07, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the two-day shoot, Cruise did not drive to the location.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He flew his own helicopter to our helipad right on top \\u2026 of the Hollywood sign here,\\\" Zarrinnam revealed.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1868, \"end\": 1882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the special moment, the movie star was able to do something that typically is not allowed.\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Normally when there is filming done up here, no one is allowed to touch the Hollywood sign,\\\" Zarrinnam said.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2084, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This was the first time that the Hollywood sign was actually touched.\\\"\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The glitz, glamour and over-the-top handoff to Los Angeles served as a preview of what's to come once the Summer Games arrive in the City of Angels in 2028.\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.356346244491172e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}]}"